The paper discusses the use of Bayesian networks for market research, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with data analysis and segmentation, which falls under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the reduction of questions asked to customers, which can be seen as a privacy concern and falls under the category of cryptography (cs.CR). Finally, the paper deals with the application of the proposed approach to broadband customers, which can be seen as a topic related to cyber-physical systems (cs.CY).
